Following up briefly.

One example we often share is Pipeshift, which moved from Pre-Seed in 2023
to Seed in 2024, with the founder highlighting our support on GTM and their
Y Combinator journey. That hands-on, cross-border support is a core part of
how we work with founders.

If helpful, I can send a concise overview or we can set up a short call to
exchange perspectives.

Talk soon,
Aabhas Khanna,
